data.description: Fantastic opportunity to live on coveted Buckeye Circle at the top of beautiful San Geronimo Valley's town of Woodacre! Enter a bright, double height foyer and a half flight up you will find the living and dining rooms with cathedral ceilings and fireplace, kitchen, two bedrooms and full bath. A sliding glass door off the dining room leads to a large covered deck for four season entertaining and extra living space overlooking the private yard backing to woods. A half flight down from the foyer are another living room, fireplace, kitchenette, two bedrooms, full bath, laundry room and large storage area with work bench. This versatile, split level floor plan provides different options: rental income, guest suite or large family home. Sited on a level, sunny lot perfect for gardening. Carport for two cars and room for additional parking, two storage sheds. Close to the Woodacre Improvement Club (pool, tennis courts, gym), two equestrian facilities and a short distance to a trail head for some of the most beautiful trails in Marin for hiking, mountain biking, horseback riding. Ten minutes to the vibrant town of Fairfax and its restaurants, shopping, seasonal farmer's market and a half hour to the beaches of Point Reyes National Seashore!
